Fixed build_conditions method.

We are creating a method dynamically:

    send("build_#{filter_type}_conditions")

The problem here is we were cleaning up params passed on the url to create
the filters with a blacklist. Now to create a filter we will verify the
param exists as a model field.

Eg. Post#status

    This will work: { :status => true }
    This will work: { :search => "title" }
    This won't work: { :published => true }
    This won't work: { :layout => "my_custom_layout" }
